  <brief_title>Molecular Epidemiology of Clostridium Difficile Infections in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Molecular Epidemiologic Survey and Risk Factor Assessment of Clostridium Difficile Infections in Children: A Focus on Recurrent and Community-associated Infections</official_title>
